OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning gives way to a
OL,6,Fsunny afternoon. Breezy northeasterly
OL,7,Fwind, especially along the coast.
OL,8,FTemperatures remain above average,
OL,9,Fthough feeling cooler by the sea.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCoastal low cloud returns
OL,12,Fonce more to affect many places
OL,13,Fovernight. Remaining dry with a gentle
OL,14,Fnortheasterly breeze, easing and
OL,15,Fbecoming light in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
