OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA cloudy morning for many,
OL,6,Fthough becoming bright with some hazy
OL,7,Fsunshine by the afternoon as the low
OL,8,Fcloud retreats to the coast. The
OL,9,Fnortheasterly breeze persists
OL,10,Fthroughout the day.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,13,Fsettled with a mix of sunny spells and
OL,14,Fcloudy periods. Breezy along the
OL,15,Fcoast. A cooling trend by the weekend
OL,16,Fbut temperatures remain above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
